<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:212'>　禮書綱目卷三十六　　　　　婺源江永撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='212:223'>地示　　　　吉禮三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='223:227'>　補</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='227:259'>天子祭天地嵗徧<span class='krp-note'>曲禮嵗此條通/言一  祭地</span>　大宗伯以黄琮禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='259:301'>地<span class='krp-note'>禮地以夏至謂神在崑崙者也/禮神者必象其類琮八方象地</span>牲幣放其器之色<span class='krp-note'>幣/以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='301:341'><span class='krp-note'>從爵若人飲酒有酬幣/春官  此條祀地玉幣</span>　　牧人陰祀用黝牲毛之<span class='krp-note'>詳/見</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='341:373'><span class='krp-note'>祭物/犧牲</span>　祭天地之牛角繭栗<span class='krp-note'>同/上</span>　犬人祭祀共犬牲用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='373:399'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-1b' );" name="038-1b" class="pb">[038-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='399:434'>牲物瘞亦如之<span class='krp-note'>同上犧此/三條  牲</span>　典瑞兩圭有邸以祀地<span class='krp-note'>兩/圭</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='434:474'><span class='krp-note'>者以象地數二也僢而同邸祀地/謂所祀於北郊神州之神  春官</span>　玉人兩圭五寸有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='474:520'>邸以祀地<span class='krp-note'>邸謂之柢有邸僢共本也車考工記禮此兩/條圭玉  酒齊粢盛器席  旗並如  天之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='520:551'><span class='krp-note'>禮/</span>　大司樂乃奏大蔟歌應鍾舞咸池以祭地示<span class='krp-note'>大蔟/陽聲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='551:590'><span class='krp-note'>第二應鍾為之合咸池大咸也地示/所祭於北郊謂神州之神及社稷</span>凡樂函鍾為宫大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='590:613'>蔟為角姑洗為徵南吕為羽靈鼓靈鼗孫竹之管空桑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='613:636'>之琴瑟咸池之舞夏日至於澤中之方丘奏之若樂八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='636:672'>變則地示皆出可得而禮矣<span class='krp-note'>地祗則主崑崙先奏是樂/以致其神禮之以玉乃後</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='672:698'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-2a' );" name="038-2a" class="pb">[038-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='698:733'><span class='krp-note'>合樂而祭之樂詳見/樂制  此條  舞</span>　大宰祀五帝則掌百官之誓戒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='733:756'>與其具脩前期十日帥執事而卜日遂戒及執事眡滌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='756:785'>濯及納亨贊王牲事及祀之日贊玉幣爵之事<span class='krp-note'>詳見天/神祀五</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='785:823'><span class='krp-note'>帝/</span>祀大示亦如之<span class='krp-note'>疏曰祀大祇謂夏至/祭地於方澤  天官</span>　大宗伯祭大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='823:846'>示帥執事而卜日宿眡滌濯涖玉鬯省牲鑊奉玉齍詔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='846:874'>大號治其大禮詔相王之大禮<span class='krp-note'>詳見/天神</span>　瘞埋於泰折祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='874:916'>地也<span class='krp-note'>折炤晢也必為炤明/之名尊神也  祭地</span>　祭地曰瘞埋<span class='krp-note'>既祭埋藏/之  爾雅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='916:946'>大祝辨六號三曰示號<span class='krp-note'>祗號若云/后土地祗</span>凡祭示則執明水火</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='946:972'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-2b' );" name="038-2b" class="pb">[038-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='972:1007'>而號祝<span class='krp-note'>詳見/天神</span>　薄薄之土承天之神<span class='krp-note'>薄旁薄也乃/順承天也</span>興甘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1007:1030'>風雨庶卉百穀莫不茂者既安且寧維予一人某敬拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1030:1067'>下土之靈維某年某月上日<span class='krp-note'>大戴禮天已上祭地禮節/其與祀  同者詳見前篇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1067:1099'>　凡以神仕者以夏日至致地示物鬽<span class='krp-note'>地物陰也陰氣/升而祭地祗物</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1099:1138'><span class='krp-note'>鬽致物鬽於墠壇盖用祭地之明日而物/之神曰鬽  詳見百神  此條祭日明日</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1138:1145'>　　右祭地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1145:1168'>王為羣姓立社曰大社王自為立社曰王社諸侯為百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1168:1191'>姓立社曰國社諸侯自為立社曰侯社大夫以下成羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1191:1217'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-3a' );" name="038-3a" class="pb">[038-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1217:1259'>立社曰置社<span class='krp-note'>羣衆也大夫以下至庶人也大夫不得特/立社與民族居百家以上則共立一社今</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1259:1295'><span class='krp-note'>時里社是也郊特牲曰唯/為社事單出里  祭法</span>　小宗伯掌建國之神位右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1295:1332'>社稷左宗廟<span class='krp-note'>庫門内雉門外/之左右  春官</span>　匠人營國左祉右社<span class='krp-note'>王/宫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1332:1361'><span class='krp-note'>所居也/考工記</span>　　乃建大社於周中其壝東青土南赤土西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1361:1390'>白土北驪土中央亹以黄土<span class='krp-note'>汲冢周書/作雒解</span>　封人掌設王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1390:1426'>之社壝<span class='krp-note'>壝謂壇及堳埓也不言稷/者稷社之細也  地官</span>　天子大社必受霜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1426:1466'>露風雨<span class='krp-note'>大社王為羣姓/所立  郊特牲</span>　小子掌珥於社稷<span class='krp-note'>鄭司農云/珥社稷以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1466:1514'><span class='krp-note'>牲頭祭也𤣥謂珥讀為衈釁禮之事也用毛牲曰刉羽/牲曰衈衈社稷謂始成其宫兆時也秋官士師職曰凡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1514:1540'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-3b' );" name="038-3b" class="pb">[038-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1540:1574'><span class='krp-note'>刉珥則奉大牲此刉/衈正字與  夏官</span>　内宰凡建國佐后立市祭之以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1574:1614'>陰禮<span class='krp-note'>祭之以陰禮者市中之社/先后所立社也  天官</span>　諸侯祭社稷<span class='krp-note'>王/制</span>　小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1614:1637'>司徒凡建邦國立其社稷　封人凡封國設其社稷之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1637:1676'>壝<span class='krp-note'>封國建諸侯大並地官之已/上天子諸侯  夫社稷  制</span>　大司徒設其社稷之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1676:1699'>壝而樹之田主各以其野之所宜木遂以名其社與其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1699:1745'>野<span class='krp-note'>社稷后土及田正之神壝壇與堳埓也田主田神后/土田正之所依也詩人謂之田祖所宜木謂若松柏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1745:1782'><span class='krp-note'>栗也若以松為社者則名松/社之野以别方面  地官</span>　小宗伯若大師則帥有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1782:1821'>司而立軍社奉主車<span class='krp-note'>有司大祝也王出軍必先有事於/社及遷廟而以其主行社主曰軍</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1821:1847'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-4a' );" name="038-4a" class="pb">[038-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1847:1894'><span class='krp-note'>社遷主曰祖春秋傳曰軍行祓社釁鼓祝奉以從曽子/問曰天子巡守以遷廟主行載於齊車言必有尊也書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1894:1939'><span class='krp-note'>曰用命賞于祖不用命戮于社社之主盖用/石為之奉謂將行  春官  已上社木社主</span>　厲山氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1939:1962'>之有天下也其子曰農能殖百穀夏之衰也周棄繼之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1962:1985'>故祀以為稷共工氏之霸九州也其子曰后土能平九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1985:2026'>州故祀以為社<span class='krp-note'>厲山氏炎帝也起於厲山或曰有烈山/氏棄后稷名也共工氏無録而王謂之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='2026:2064'><span class='krp-note'>霸在大昊炎帝/之間  祭法</span>　共工氏有子曰句龍為后土<span class='krp-note'>共工在/大昊後</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2064:2107'><span class='krp-note'>神農前以水名官者其子句/龍能平水土故死而見祀</span>后土為社<span class='krp-note'>方答社稷故/明言為社</span>稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2107:2142'>田正也<span class='krp-note'>掌播/殖也</span>有烈山氏之子曰柱為稷<span class='krp-note'>烈山氏神農/世為諸侯</span>自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2142:2168'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-4b' );" name="038-4b" class="pb">[038-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2168:2208'>夏以上祀之<span class='krp-note'>祀/柱</span>周棄亦為稷<span class='krp-note'>棄周之始祖能播百穀湯/既勝夏廢柱而以棄代之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2208:2242'>自商以來祀之<span class='krp-note'>昭二十九年左氏傳/  已上社稷配祭</span>　季夏命四監大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2242:2265'>合百縣之秩芻以養犧牲令民無不咸出其力以祠社</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2265:2288'>稷之靈以為民祈福季冬乃命大史次諸侯之烈賦之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2288:2311'>犧牲以共社稷之饗凡在天下九州之民者無不咸獻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2311:2340'>其力以共社稷之祀<span class='krp-note'>詳見祭/物犧牲</span>　天子社稷皆大牢諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2340:2375'>社稷皆少牢<span class='krp-note'>王/制</span>　牧人陰祀用黝牲毛之<span class='krp-note'>陰祀祭地北/郊及社稷也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2375:2408'><span class='krp-note'>鄭司農云黝讀為/幽黑也  地官</span>　大司馬中春教振旅遂以蒐田獻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2408:2434'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-5a' );" name="038-5a" class="pb">[038-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2434:2468'>禽以祭社<span class='krp-note'>春田主祭社者土/方施生也  夏官</span>　鬯人凡祭祀社壝用大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2468:2507'>壘<span class='krp-note'>壝謂委土為墠壇所/以祭也大壘瓦壘</span>　司服祭社稷則希冕<span class='krp-note'>希刺粉/米無畫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2507:2541'><span class='krp-note'>也其衣一章裳二章/凡三也  並春官</span>　大司樂乃奏大蔟歌應鍾舞咸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2541:2577'>池以祭地示<span class='krp-note'>詳見/祭地</span>　鼓人以靈鼓鼓社祭<span class='krp-note'>靈鼓六面鼔/也社祭祭地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2577:2614'><span class='krp-note'>祗/也</span>　舞師教帗舞帥而舞社稷之祭祀<span class='krp-note'>疏曰帗舞用五/色繒  並地官</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2614:2656'><span class='krp-note'>物已上禮/  樂舞</span>　封人令社稷之職<span class='krp-note'>將祭之時令諸有職事/於社稷者也郊特牲曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2656:2704'><span class='krp-note'>唯為社事單出里唯為社田國人畢作唯/社丘乗共粢盛所以報本反始也  地官</span>　春社<span class='krp-note'>春田/祭社</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2704:2742'><span class='krp-note'>大司馬職云/  明堂位</span>　社祭土日用甲<span class='krp-note'>國中之神/莫貴於社</span>君南鄉於北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2742:2768'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-5b' );" name="038-5b" class="pb">[038-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2768:2805'>墉下<span class='krp-note'>牆謂之墉北墉社内北牆/  郊特牲  詳見祭義</span>　大宗伯以血祭祭社</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2805:2851'>稷<span class='krp-note'>不言祭地此皆地祇祭地可知也陰祀自血起貴氣/臭也社稷土穀之神有徳者配食焉共工氏之子曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2851:2898'><span class='krp-note'>句龍食於社有厲山氏之子曰柱/食於稷湯遷之而祀棄  春官</span>　三獻文<span class='krp-note'>謂祭社稷/五祀  禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2898:2938'><span class='krp-note'>器/</span>　三獻爓<span class='krp-note'>疏曰社又降於宗廟故用/爓爓人稍近味  郊特牲</span>　肆師社之日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2938:2979'>涖卜來嵗之稼<span class='krp-note'>社祭土為取財焉卜者問後嵗稼/所宜  春官  已上祭社稷禮節</span>　䘮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2979:3019'>國之社屋之薄社北牖<span class='krp-note'>絶其陽通其陰而已薄社殷之/社殷始都薄  郊特牲  詳見</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='3019:3050'><span class='krp-note'>祭/義</span>　䘮祝掌勝國邑之社稷之祝號以祭祀禱祠焉<span class='krp-note'>勝/國</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='3050:3093'><span class='krp-note'>邑所誅討者社稷者若亳社是已存之者重/神也盖奄其上而棧其下為北牖  春官</span>　士師若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='3093:3119'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-6a' );" name="038-6a" class="pb">[038-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3119:3158'>祭勝國之社稷則為之尸<span class='krp-note'>以刑官為尸略之也周謂亡/殷之社為亳社  秋官  已</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3158:3198'><span class='krp-note'>上勝國/社稷</span>　仲春擇元日命民社<span class='krp-note'>社后土也使民祀焉神/其農業也祀社日用甲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3198:3224'><span class='krp-note'>令月/</span>　州長若以嵗時祭祀州社則屬其民而讀法凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3224:3255'>州之大祭祀涖其事<span class='krp-note'>大祭祀謂州社/稷也涖臨也</span>　閭胥凡春秋之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3255:3289'>祭祀聚衆庶既比則讀法<span class='krp-note'>祭祀謂州社黨禜/族酺也  並地官</span>　肆師若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3289:3322'>國有大故則令國人祭<span class='krp-note'>大故謂水旱凶荒所/令祭者社及禜酺</span>嵗時之祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3322:3355'>祀亦如之<span class='krp-note'>月令仲春命民社/此一隅  春官</span>　唯為社事單出里唯為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3355:3389'>社田國人畢作唯社丘乗共粢盛<span class='krp-note'>單出里皆徃祭社於/都鄙二十五家為里</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3389:3415'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-6b' );" name="038-6b" class="pb">[038-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3415:3462'><span class='krp-note'>畢作人則盡行非徒羡也丘十六井也四丘六十四井/曰甸或謂之乗乗者以千車賦出長轂一乗乗或為鄰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3462:3484'><span class='krp-note'>祭郊特牲上詳見/  義  已  民社</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3484:3511'>　　右祭社稷　湯既勝夏欲遷其社不可作夏社<span class='krp-note'>湯/承</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3511:3556'>　　<span class='krp-note'>堯舜禪代之後順天應人逆取順守而有慙徳故/革命創制改正易服變置社稷而後世無及句龍</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3556:3595'>　　<span class='krp-note'>者故不可而/止  書序</span>　迺立冢土戎醜攸行<span class='krp-note'>冢土大社也/亦大王所立</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3595:3639'>　　<span class='krp-note'>而後因以為天子之制也戎醜大衆也起大事/動大衆必有事乎社而後出謂之宜  大雅緜</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3639:3662'>　　哀公問社於宰我宰我對曰夏后氏以松殷人以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3662:3697'>　　柏周人以栗曰使民戰栗<span class='krp-note'>宰我孔子弟子名予三/代之社不同者古者立</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3697:3723'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-7a' );" name="038-7a" class="pb">[038-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3723:3768'>　　<span class='krp-note'>社各樹其土之所宜木以為主也戰栗恐懼貌宰/我又言周所以用栗之意如此豈以古者戮人於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3768:3797'>　　<span class='krp-note'>社故附㑹/其説與</span>子聞之曰成事不説遂事不諫既徃不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3797:3841'>　　咎<span class='krp-note'>遂事謂事雖未成而勢不能已者孔子以宰我/所對非立社之本意又啓時君殺伐之心而其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3841:3886'>　　<span class='krp-note'>言已出不可復救故厯言此以深責之欲使謹其/後也尹氏曰古者各以所宜木名其社非取義於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3886:3921'>　　<span class='krp-note'>木也宰我不知而妄對/故夫子責之  論語</span>　尚書亡篇曰太社唯松</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3921:3944'>　　東社唯柏南社唯梓西社唯栗北社唯槐春秋文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3944:3967'>　　義曰天子之社稷廣五丈諸侯半之春秋傳曰天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3967:3990'>　　子有大社焉東方青土南方赤土西方白土北方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3990:4016'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-7b' );" name="038-7b" class="pb">[038-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='4016:4039'>　　黑土上冒以黄土故將封東方諸侯青土苴以白</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='4039:4074'>　　茅<span class='krp-note'>白虎/通</span>　春社天子之祭也<span class='krp-note'>春田祭社/  明堂位</span>　載芟春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='4074:4101'>　　藉田而祈社稷也　良耜秋報社稷也<span class='krp-note'>並詩/序</span>　以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='4101:4135'>　　我齊明與我犧羊以社以方<span class='krp-note'>齊與粢同曲禮曰稷/曰明粢此言齊明便</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='4135:4180'>　　<span class='krp-note'>文以協韵耳犧羊純色之羊也社后土也以句龍/氏配方秋祭四方報成萬物周禮所謂羅弊獻禽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='4180:4212'>　　<span class='krp-note'>以祀祊是也/  小雅甫田</span>　曽子問曰諸侯之祭社稷俎豆既</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='4212:4235'>　　陳聞天子崩后之䘮君薨夫人之䘮如之何孔子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4235:4262'>　　曰廢自薨比至於殯自啟至於反哭奉帥天子<span class='krp-note'>詳/見</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4262:4288'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-8a' );" name="038-8a" class="pb">[038-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4288:4322'>　　<span class='krp-note'>祭通禮/廢祭章</span>　孟子曰民為貴社稷次之君為輕<span class='krp-note'>社土/神稷</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4322:4367'>　　<span class='krp-note'>穀神建國則立壇壝以祀之盖國以民為本社稷/亦為民而立而君之尊又係於二者之存亡故其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4367:4407'>　　<span class='krp-note'>輕重/如此</span>諸侯危社稷則變置<span class='krp-note'>諸侯無道將使社稷為/人所滅則當更立賢君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4407:4436'>　　<span class='krp-note'>是君輕於/社稷也</span>犧牲既成粢盛既潔祭祀以時然而旱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4436:4473'>　　乾水溢則變置社稷<span class='krp-note'>祭祀不失禮而土穀之神不/能為民禦灾捍患則毁其壇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4473:4513'>　　<span class='krp-note'>壝而更置之亦年不順成八蜡不通/之意是社稷雖重於君而輕於民也</span>　鄭子産伐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4513:4548'>　　陳入之陳侯免擁社<span class='krp-note'>免䘮服擁社抱社主示服/  襄二十五年左氏傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4548:4582'>　　哀公四年六月辛丑亳社灾<span class='krp-note'>杜曰天火也亳社殷/社諸侯有之所以戒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4582:4608'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-8b' );" name="038-8b" class="pb">[038-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4608:4654'>　　<span class='krp-note'>亡國以范曰殷都於亳武王克紂而班列其社於/諸侯  為亡國之戒劉向曰灾亳社戒人君縱恣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='4654:4691'>　　<span class='krp-note'>不能警戒之/象  春秋</span>亳社者亳之社也亳亡國也<span class='krp-note'>亳即殷/也殷都</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='4691:4729'>　　<span class='krp-note'>於亳故國/謂之亳社</span>亡國之社以為廟屏戒也<span class='krp-note'>立亳之社於/廟之外以為</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='4729:4763'>　　<span class='krp-note'>屏蔽取其不得通天/人君瞻之而致戒心</span>其屋亡國之社不得達上也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='4763:4800'>　　<span class='krp-note'>必為之作屋不使上通天也/縁有屋故言灾  穀梁傳</span>　蒲社灾蒲社者何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='4800:4838'>　　<span class='krp-note'>據鼓用牲於/社不言蒲</span>亡國之社也<span class='krp-note'>蒲社者先世之/亡國在魯竟</span>社者封</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='4838:4873'>　　也<span class='krp-note'>封土/為社</span>其言灾何<span class='krp-note'>據封土非/火所能燒</span>亡國之社盖揜之揜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='4873:4911'>　　其上而柴其下<span class='krp-note'>故火得燒之揜柴之者絶不得/使通天地四方以為有國者戒</span>蒲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4911:4937'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-9a' );" name="038-9a" class="pb">[038-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4937:4974'>　　社灾何以書記灾也<span class='krp-note'>戒社者先王之所以威示教/戒諸侯使事上也灾者象諸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4974:5020'>　　<span class='krp-note'>侯背天子是後宋事彊吴齊晉前驅滕薛俠轂魯/衞驂乗故天去戒社若曰王教滅絶云耳  公羊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='5020:5059'>　　<span class='krp-note'>傳/</span>　莊公如齊觀社<span class='krp-note'>莊公二十三年齊因祀社/蒐軍實以示客公徃觀之</span>曹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='5059:5087'>　　劌諫曰不可夫齊棄大公之法而觀民於社<span class='krp-note'>大公/齊始</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='5087:5123'>　　<span class='krp-note'>祖大公/望也</span>君為是舉<span class='krp-note'>舉動/也</span>而徃觀之非故業也<span class='krp-note'>業事/也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='5123:5160'>　　何以訓民土𤼵而社助時也<span class='krp-note'>土𤼵春分也周語曰/土乃脈𤼵社者助時</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='5160:5201'>　　<span class='krp-note'>求福為/農始也</span>收攟而烝納要也<span class='krp-note'>攟拾也冬祭曰烝因祭/社以納五穀之要休農</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='5201:5236'>　　<span class='krp-note'>夫也月令曰孟冬祀於天/宗大祀於公社及門閭</span>今齊社而徃觀旅非先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='5236:5262'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-9b' );" name="038-9b" class="pb">[038-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='5262:5294'>　　王之訓也<span class='krp-note'>旅衆/也</span>天子祀上帝<span class='krp-note'>上帝上/天也</span>諸侯㑹之受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='5294:5333'>　　命焉<span class='krp-note'>助祭受/政命也</span>諸侯祀先王先公<span class='krp-note'>先王謂若宋祖帝/乙鄭祖厲王之屬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='5333:5367'>　　<span class='krp-note'>也先公/先君也</span>卿大夫佐之受事焉<span class='krp-note'>事職/事也</span>臣不聞諸侯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5367:5394'>　　相㑹祀也祀又不法<span class='krp-note'>不法謂觀民也/  國語魯語</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5394:5417'>王為羣姓立七祀曰司命曰中霤曰國門曰國行曰泰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='5417:5440'>厲曰戸曰竈王自為立七祀諸侯為國立五祀曰司命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='5440:5463'>曰中霤曰國門曰國行曰公厲諸侯自為立五祀大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='5463:5486'>立三祀曰族厲曰門曰行適士立二祀曰門曰行庶士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='5486:5513'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-10a' );" name="038-10a" class="pb">[038-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='5513:5549'>庶人立一祀或立户或立竈<span class='krp-note'>此非大神所祈報大事者/也小神居人之間司察小</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5549:5596'><span class='krp-note'>過作譴告者爾樂記曰明則有禮樂幽則有鬼神鬼神/謂此與司命主督察三命中霤主堂室居處門户主出</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='5596:5643'><span class='krp-note'>入行主道路行作厲主殺伐竈主飲食之事明堂月令/春曰其祀戸祭先脾夏曰其祀竈祭先肺中央曰其祀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='5643:5690'><span class='krp-note'>中霤祭先心秋曰其祀門祭先肝冬曰其祀行祭先腎/聘禮曰使者出釋幣於行歸釋幣於門士喪禮曰疾病</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='5690:5737'><span class='krp-note'>禱於五祀司命與厲其時不著今時民家或春秋祀司/命行神山神門户竈在旁是必春祠司命秋祠厲也或</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='5737:5782'><span class='krp-note'>者合而祠之山即厲也民惡言厲巫祝以厲山為/之謬乎春秋傳曰鬼有所歸乃不為厲  祭法</span>　小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='5782:5824'>子掌祈於五祀<span class='krp-note'>故書祀作禩鄭司農云禩讀為祀書亦/或為祀𤣥謂祈或為刉用毛牲曰刉刉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='5824:5861'><span class='krp-note'>者釁禮之事也刉五祀謂/始成其宫兆時也  夏官</span>　天子祭五祀嵗徧諸侯祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='5861:5888'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-10b' );" name="038-10b" class="pb">[038-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='5888:5924'>五祀嵗徧大夫祭五祀嵗徧<span class='krp-note'>五祀户竈中霤門行也此/盖殷時制也祭法曰天子</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='5924:5969'><span class='krp-note'>立七祀諸侯立五祀大夫立三/祀士立二祀謂周制也  曲禮</span>　大夫祭五祀<span class='krp-note'>五祀謂/司命也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='5969:6013'><span class='krp-note'>中霤也門也行也厲也此祭謂大/夫有地者其無地祭三耳  王制</span>　春祀户祭先脾<span class='krp-note'>春/陽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='6013:6060'><span class='krp-note'>氣出祀之於戸内陽也祀之先祭脾者春為陽中於藏/直脾脾為尊凡祭五祀於廟用特牲有主有尸皆先設</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='6060:6107'><span class='krp-note'>席於奥祀户之禮南面設主於户内之西乃制脾及腎/為俎奠於主北又設盛於俎西祭黍稷祭肉祭醴皆三</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='6107:6151'><span class='krp-note'>祭肉脾一腎再既祭徹之更陳鼎俎/設饌於筵前迎尸略如祭宗廟之儀</span>夏祀竈祭先肺<span class='krp-note'>夏/陽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='6151:6198'><span class='krp-note'>氣盛熱於外祀之於竈從熱類也祀之祭先肺者陽位/在上肺亦在上肺為尊也竈在廟門外之東祀竈之禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='6198:6245'><span class='krp-note'>先席於門之奥東面設主於竈陘乃制肺及心肝為俎/奠於主西又設盛於俎南亦祭黍三祭肺心肝各一祭</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='6245:6272'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-11a' );" name="038-11a" class="pb">[038-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='6272:6313'><span class='krp-note'>醴三亦既祭徹之更陳鼎俎設/饌於筵前迎尸如祀户之禮</span>中央祀中霤祭先心<span class='krp-note'>中/霤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='6313:6360'><span class='krp-note'>猶中室也土主中央而神在室古者複穴是以名室為/霤云祀之先祭心者五藏之次心次肺至此心為尊也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='6360:6402'><span class='krp-note'>祀中霤之禮設主於牖下乃制心及肝肺/為俎其祭肉心肺肝各一他如祀户之禮</span>秋祀門祭先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='6402:6448'>肝<span class='krp-note'>秋陰氣出祀之於門外陰也祀之先祭肝者秋為陰/中於藏直肝肝為尊也祀門之禮北面設主於門左</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='6448:6491'><span class='krp-note'>樞乃制肝及肺心為俎奠於主南又/設盛於俎東其他皆如祭竈之禮</span>冬祀行祭先腎<span class='krp-note'>冬/陰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='6491:6538'><span class='krp-note'>盛寒於水祀之於行從辟除之類也祀之先祭腎者陰/位在下腎亦在下腎為尊也行在廟門外之西為軷壤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='6538:6585'><span class='krp-note'>厚二寸廣五尺輪四尺祀行之禮北面設主於軷上乃/制腎及脾為俎奠於主南又設盛於俎東祭肉腎一脾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='6585:6626'><span class='krp-note'>再其他皆如祀/門之禮  月令</span>　大宗伯以血祭祭五祀<span class='krp-note'>陰祀自血起/貴氣臭也故</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='6626:6653'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-11b' );" name="038-11b" class="pb">[038-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='6653:6701'><span class='krp-note'>書祀作禩鄭司農云禩當為祀書亦或作祀五祀五色/之帝於王者宫中曰五祀𤣥謂此五祀者五官之神在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='6701:6748'><span class='krp-note'>四郊四時迎五行之氣於四郊而祭五徳之帝亦食此/神焉少昊氏之子曰重為句芒食於木該為蓐收食於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='6748:6788'><span class='krp-note'>金脩及熈為𤣥㝠食於水顓頊氏/之子曰黎為祝融后土食於火土</span>　司服祭五祀則希</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='6788:6827'>冕<span class='krp-note'>注見祭社稷/章  春官</span>　三獻文<span class='krp-note'>謂祭社稷五/祀  禮器</span>　司門凡嵗時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='6827:6867'>之門受其餘<span class='krp-note'>鄭司農云受祭/門之餘  地官</span>　孟冬臘五祀<span class='krp-note'>臘謂以田/獵所得禽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='6867:6887'><span class='krp-note'>祭也五祀門戸中/霤竈行也  月令</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='6887:6910'>　　右祭五祀　天子崩未殯五祀之祭不行既殯而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='6910:6933'>　　祭其祭也尸入三飯不侑酳不酢而已矣自啟至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='6933:6960'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-12a' );" name="038-12a" class="pb">[038-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='6960:6987'>　　於反哭五祀之祭不行已葬而祭祝畢獻而已<span class='krp-note'>既/葬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='6987:7019'>　　<span class='krp-note'>彌吉畢獻祝而後止郊社亦然/唯嘗禘宗廟俟吉也  曽子問</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='7019:7053'>小宗伯兆五帝於四郊四望亦如之<span class='krp-note'>鄭司農云四望道/氣出入𤣥謂四望</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='7053:7089'><span class='krp-note'>五嶽四鎮四/竇  春官</span>　牧人望祀各以其方之色牲毛之<span class='krp-note'>望祀/五嶽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='7089:7131'><span class='krp-note'>四鎮四瀆/也  地官</span>　司服祀四望則毳冕<span class='krp-note'>毳畫虎蜼謂宗彛也/其衣三章裳二章凡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='7131:7166'><span class='krp-note'>五/也</span>　典瑞兩圭有邸旅四望<span class='krp-note'>注見祭地/  並春官</span>　玉人兩圭五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='7166:7197'>寸有邸旅四望<span class='krp-note'>注見祭地/  考工記</span>　大司樂乃奏姑洗歌南吕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='7197:7232'>舞大㲈以祀四望<span class='krp-note'>姑洗陽聲第三南吕為之/合四望五嶽四鎮四竇</span>　大祝國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='7232:7259'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-12b' );" name="038-12b" class="pb">[038-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='7259:7297'>將有事於四望則前祝<span class='krp-note'>前祝者王出也歸也將有事於/此神大祝居前先以祝辭告之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='7297:7328'><span class='krp-note'>春並/  官</span>　五獻察<span class='krp-note'>察明也謂祭四望/山川也  禮器</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='7328:7351'>　　右祀四望　三正記曰郊後必有望　僖公三十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='7351:7380'>　　一年夏四月四卜郊不從乃免牲猶三望<span class='krp-note'>三望分/野之星</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='7380:7421'>　　<span class='krp-note'>國中山川皆因郊祀望而祭之魯廢郊/天而脩其小祀故曰猶猶者可止之辭</span>猶三望亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='7421:7452'>　　非禮也望郊之細也不郊亦無望可也<span class='krp-note'>春秋左氏/傳  宣三</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='7452:7492'>　　<span class='krp-note'>年傳云望/郊之屬也</span>　天子有方望之事<span class='krp-note'>方望謂郊時所望/祭四方羣神日月</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='7492:7535'>　　<span class='krp-note'>星辰風伯雨師五嶽四瀆/及餘山川凡三十六所</span>無所不通<span class='krp-note'>盡八極之内/天之所覆地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='7535:7562'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-13a' );" name="038-13a" class="pb">[038-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='7562:7593'>　　<span class='krp-note'>之所戴無所不/至故得郊也</span>諸侯山川有不在其封内者則不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='7593:7622'>　　祭也<span class='krp-note'>故魯郊/非禮也</span>三望者何望祭也然則曷祭祭泰山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='7622:7645'>　　河海曷為祭泰山河海山川有能潤於百里者天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='7645:7685'>　　子秩而祭之<span class='krp-note'>此皆助天宣氣布功故祭天及之秩/者隨其大小尊卑髙下所宜禮祭天</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='7685:7730'>　　<span class='krp-note'>牲角繭栗社稷宗廟角握六宗五嶽四瀆角尺其/餘山川視卿大夫天燎地瘞日月星辰布山縣水</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='7730:7768'>　　<span class='krp-note'>沈風磔雨升燎者取俎上七體與/其珪寳在辨中置於柴上燒之</span>觸石而出膚寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='7768:7805'>　　而合<span class='krp-note'>側手為膚案指為寸言其觸/石理而興無有膚寸而不合</span>不崇朝而徧雨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='7805:7836'>　　乎天下者唯泰山爾<span class='krp-note'>崇重也不重/朝言一朝也</span>河海潤於千里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='7836:7863'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-13b' );" name="038-13b" class="pb">[038-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='7863:7908'>　　<span class='krp-note'>亦能通氣致雨潤澤及於千里韓詩説曰湯時大/旱使人禱山川是也郊望非一獨祭三者魯郊非</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='7908:7937'>　　<span class='krp-note'>禮故獨祭/其大者</span>猶者何通可以已也何以書譏不郊而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='7937:7974'>　　望祭也<span class='krp-note'>譏尊者不食而卑者獨食/書者惡失禮也  公羊傳</span>　楚昭王曰三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='7974:8005'>　　代命祀祭不越望<span class='krp-note'>諸侯望祀竟/内山川星辰</span>江漢睢章楚之望</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='8005:8035'>　　也<span class='krp-note'>四水在楚界六詳見因祭/疾病章  哀  年左氏傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='8035:8065'>小宗伯兆山川丘陵墳衍各因其方<span class='krp-note'>順其所在/  春官</span>　天子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='8065:8092'>諸侯祭山川嵗徧<span class='krp-note'>曲/禮</span>　天子祭天下名山大川五嶽視</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='8092:8133'>三公四瀆視諸侯<span class='krp-note'>視視其牲器之數諸尚書大傳云五/嶽視三公四瀆視  侯其餘山川視</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='8133:8160'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-14a' );" name="038-14a" class="pb">[038-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='8160:8198'><span class='krp-note'>伯小者視子男注云謂其牲幣/粢盛籩豆爵獻之數非謂尊卑</span>諸侯祭名山大川之在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='8198:8232'>其地者<span class='krp-note'>魯人祭泰山晉人/祭河是也  王制</span>　孟春命祀山林川澤犧牲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='8232:8261'>毋用牝<span class='krp-note'>為傷姙/生之類</span>　仲冬天子命有司祈祀四海大川名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='8261:8294'>源淵澤井泉<span class='krp-note'>順其徳盛之時祭之/也今月令淵為深</span>　季冬乃畢山川之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='8294:8330'>祀<span class='krp-note'>四時之功成於冬孟月祭/其宗至此可以祭其佐也</span>命宰厯卿大夫至於庶民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='8330:8361'>土田之數而賦犧牲以共山林名川之祀<span class='krp-note'>此所與卿大/夫庶民共者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='8361:8403'><span class='krp-note'>也厯猶次也卿大夫采地亦有大小其非/采地以其邑之名多少賦之  並月令</span>　羊人凡沈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='8403:8439'>共其羊牲　小子凡沈飾其牲<span class='krp-note'>鄭司農云沈謂祭川爾/雅曰祭川曰浮沉  並</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='8439:8466'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-14b' );" name="038-14b" class="pb">[038-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='8466:8501'><span class='krp-note'>夏/官</span>　犬人掌犬牲凡沈用駹可也<span class='krp-note'>駹謂不純色/也  秋官</span>　司服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='8501:8534'>祀山川則毳冕<span class='krp-note'>注見祀/四望</span>　典瑞璋邸射以祀山川<span class='krp-note'>璋有/邸而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='8534:8569'><span class='krp-note'>射取殺於四望鄭司農/云射剡也  並春官</span>　玉人璋邸射素功以祀山川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='8569:8611'><span class='krp-note'>邸射剡而出也鄭司農云/素功無飾也  考工記</span>　鬯人凡山川用蜃<span class='krp-note'>蜃畫為/蜃形蚌</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='8611:8642'><span class='krp-note'>曰含漿尊之/象  春官</span>　大司樂乃奏蕤賓歌函鐘舞大夏以祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='8642:8679'>山川<span class='krp-note'>蕤賓陽聲第四函鐘為之/合函鐘一名林鐘  同上</span>　舞師掌教兵舞帥而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='8679:8702'>舞山川之祭祀　山虞若祭山林則為主而脩除且蹕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='8702:8738'><span class='krp-note'>為主主辨䕶之也脩除/治道路場壇  並春官</span>　大宗伯以血祭祭五嶽以貍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='8738:8765'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-15a' );" name="038-15a" class="pb">[038-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='8765:8807'>沈祭山川澤<span class='krp-note'>陰祀自血起貴氣臭也五嶽東曰岱宗南/曰衡山西曰華山北曰恒山中曰嵩髙山</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='8807:8850'><span class='krp-note'>不見四竇者四竇五嶽之匹或省文祭山/林曰埋川澤曰沈順其性之含藏  春官</span>　祭山曰庪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='8850:8894'>縣<span class='krp-note'>或庪或縣置之於山山/海經曰縣以吉玉是也</span>祭川曰浮沈<span class='krp-note'>投祭水中或浮/或沈  爾雅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='8894:8928'>　三王之祭川也皆先河而後海<span class='krp-note'>學/記</span>　五獻察<span class='krp-note'>注見四/望  禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='8928:8960'><span class='krp-note'>器/</span>　山川之神則水旱癘疫之灾於是乎禜之<span class='krp-note'>詳見因/祭疾病</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='8960:8987'>　　右祭山川　周公祀泰山召公為尸<span class='krp-note'>白虎/通</span>　晉人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='8987:9021'>　　將有事於河必先有事於惡池<span class='krp-note'>惡當為呼聲之誤也/呼池嘔夷并州川</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='9021:9051'>　　齊人將有事於泰山必先有事於配林<span class='krp-note'>配林林名/  禮器</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='9051:9078'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '038-15b' );" name="038-15b" class="pb">[038-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='9078:9101'>　　　季氏旅於泰山子謂冉有曰女弗能救與對曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='9101:9131'>　　不能子曰嗚乎曾謂泰山不如林放乎<span class='krp-note'>旅祭名㤗/山山名在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='9131:9176'>　　<span class='krp-note'>魯地禮諸侯祭封内山川季氏祭之僭也冉有孔/子弟子名求時為季氏宰救謂救其陷於僭竊之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='9176:9217'>　　<span class='krp-note'>罪嗚呼歎辭言神不享非禮欲季氏知其無/益而自止又進林放以厲冉有也  論語</span></span><br/>
